high_descs: Turn right then face the black table to your left.
Take the keys off of the table in front of you.
Turn left then face the white safe to your right.
Place the keys inside the safe in front of you and close it.
Turn around then face the couch to your right.
Take the keys from the couch in front of you.
Turn right and face the safe in front of you.
Place the keys in the safe in front of you.
Turn right to move to stand in front of the black console table against the wall.
Pick up the keys from the front right corner of the table.
Turn around and cross the room to the sofa and then turn right to face the small white safe on the ground.
Put the keys inside the safe and shut the door.
Turn left and move to stand in front of the sofa.
Pick up the keys from the cushion of the sofa closest to the wall with the safe.
Turn right and move back to stand in front of the white safe.
Open the safe, put the keys inside, and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Move two sets of keys to the white safe.
